OL,5, People should go into some stores      
OL,6, rather than rely on online shopping if 
OL,7, they want to get Christmas gifts on    
OL,8, time, retailers have said, as postal   
OL,9, strikes delay parcel deliveries.       
OL,11,F"That's the advice we're giving," the  
OL,12,Fboss of bookseller Waterstones said.   
OL,14,FIf buying from smaller retailers,      
OL,15,Fshopping in store will ensure          
OL,16,F"certainty", the British Independent   
OL,17,FRetailers Association (Bira) said.     
